{"tid":2355471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賤種藍屍四頁文字文宣 開始周圍派店鋪","createTime":"2021-01-06T06:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T09:43:13.000Z","uid":143023,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b06cf0db519cd0fd73fbea295b819db9fa7c7716","tid":2355471,"uid":143023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T06:35:02.000Z","msg":"小弟喺某黃店做緊<br />\n話說今日收收下銀 有條柒碌中年男人 就咁放低呢份嘢就走咗去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cNWaLKj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcNWaLKj.png&h=df27b7d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MuFbva4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMuFbva4.png&h=1f95f4ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6PjceCP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6PjceCP.png&h=fc19f3d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/68maLKz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F68maLKz.png&h=e43b5e34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母睇睇下 邊撚個張德盛<br />\n<br />\n各位，今日港共賤種+一堆含撚黑狗 已經踩到唔係上心口，係踩到上個頭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家究竟要幾時先醒覺 做實事， 唔係食黃店 接納奶共明星 批鬥自己人啊！<br />\n<br />\n班柒頭賤種落地獄就緊，但係要靠我地親手送作地啊！<br />\n<br />\n利申：即刻追出去條柒頭已經啊唔知竄咗去邊，大家甩到一定要捉撚住佢嚟示眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"906389eb2a3a6a1024297c8076fb5ff3e8269189","tid":2355471,"uid":35774,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T06:36:58.000Z","msg":"條友似妄想被迫害喎"},{"pid":"b34602b07a1a438336fd0e0c9b6c6414464b06d2","tid":2355471,"uid":143023,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"906389eb2a3a6a1024297c8076fb5ff3e8269189","tid":2355471,"uid":35774,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T06:36:58.000Z","msg":"條友似妄想被迫害喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T06:38:31.000Z","msg":"有邊個藍屍唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"